efault/files/pictures/alex.png\" style=\"float:right\" width=\"134\" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rteindent1\">ECE undergraduate, moved on to a Master\'s at the CMU Robotics Institute.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Vitchyr Pong</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rteindent1\">Undergraduate in ECE and CS, moved on to a PhD at UC Berkeley.<img alt=\"\" height=\"175\" src=\"/sites/default/files/pictures/vitchyr.jpg\" style=\"float:right\" width=\"263\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,3,3,'und',0,'<p>Publications to go here.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,4,4,'und',0,'<p>Links to project pages to go here</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','news',0,6,6,'und',0,'<p>This is a fake new story about exciting things the lab has accomplished. Real content will go here once the formatting is done.</p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,7,7,'und',0,'<h1 class=\"rtecenter\">Cornell Robotic Personal Assistants Lab</h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"rtecenter\">The Cornell Robotic Personal Assistants Lab is focused on advancing the state of the art&nbsp;in HRI, robotic manipulation, and multi-agent planning and coordination.</p>\r\n','','full_html');
